{"tid":1371144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺大馬路觀察十分鐘我見","createTime":"2019-07-27T07:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T08:16:09.000Z","uid":14423,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66ef8092c17a6bc5a212645094a4ee4b60538088","tid":1371144,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"先利伸：元朗人<br />\n大馬路開始多人<br />\n有啲由元朗站去警署<br />\n有啲由警署去元朗<br />\n兩邊行嘅方向相反<br />\n但大家都無分行邊條馬路<br />\n之前都仲行到<br />\n但依家開始有啲塞<br />\n所以建議警署/朗屏出發嘅，行往博愛方向嘅馬路<br />\n而元朗站出發，行向天水圍屯門方向"},{"pid":"08d98eb938184dd21aeffc4f9802eccac0be855b","tid":1371144,"uid":267801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"大家自由閪"},{"pid":"28d16d508f245b486e5bdd62fc1e8006ba3f5f19","tid":1371144,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"覺得認同嘅歡迎幫推，方便啲人遊行<br />\n唔認同就由佢沉算，俾其他post上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc93e0b97ad84f410b7b600466f27c2d257ce35","tid":1371144,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"推多幾下算"},{"pid":"b7998352063c3031a545fcb5dbe8bd45a0f4b4ca","tid":1371144,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:58:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1126b913251ff6b09eee46c02c472c494df129f9","tid":1371144,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:00:54.000Z","msg":"再推多下"},{"pid":"0cfbcec7a2222018eb6c44366410e4a4a2f1e67c","tid":1371144,"uid":271407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"db52be4530b511b3860a0f5048c845a2320569b9","tid":1371144,"uid":172321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c421a778aabcae898e68c49ae8df8e7b27c760c","tid":1371144,"uid":172321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:02:57.000Z